"title": "2066: Jesus Christ, power of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2066: jesus christ, power of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The historical and ongoing effective authority of Jesus Christ over natural elements, over human life and ultimately over sin, forces of evil, Satan and death.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's power is from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God's creative power is exercised through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16\">COL 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>God's infinite power is given to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18\">MAT 28:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6\">MAT 9:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:10\">MRK 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:24\">LUK 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:26\">MAT 19:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:37\">LUK 1:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34-John3:35\">JHN 3:34–3:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:19-John5:20\">JHN 5:19–5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:3\">JHN 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9\">PHP 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's power is revealed on earth</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:26–8:27</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:39–4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:25\">MAT 14:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:48\">MRK 6:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:19\">JHN 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:19\">MAT 21:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:14\">MRK 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:21\">MRK 11:21</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over sickness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:3\">MAT 8:2–8:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:40-Mark1:42\">MRK 1:40–1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:12-Luke5:13\">LUK 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:27-Mark5:30\">MRK 5:27–5:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:21-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:21–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:44-Luke8:46\">LUK 8:44–8:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17\">LUK 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over human life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:22\">LUK 7:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18-Matt9:25\">MAT 9:18–9:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:22-Mark5:42\">MRK 5:22–5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:41-Luke8:55\">LUK 8:41–8:55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:43-John11:44\">JHN 11:43–11:44</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over his own life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:18\">JHN 10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:16\">HEB 7:16</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over human behaviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:20\">MAT 4:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:11\">LUK 5:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:28\">LUK 5:27–5:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:5\">MRK 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:29\">JHN 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:10-John19:11\">JHN 19:10–19:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over forces of evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:16\">MAT 8:16</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:32-Mark1:34\">MRK 1:32–1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:40-Luke4:41\">LUK 4:40–4:41</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10-Matt4:11\">MAT 4:10–4:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:13\">MRK 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:12-Luke4:13\">LUK 4:12–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:32-Matt9:33\">MAT 9:32–9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:18\">MAT 17:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:25\">MRK 9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:42\">LUK 9:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:30\">JHN 14:30</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ has power over sin and death</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's crucifixion defeats the power of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:6\">ROM 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10-Isa53:12\">ISA 53:10–53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6\">MAT 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3\">1CO 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:9\">REV 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's resurrection defeats the power of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:9\">ROM 6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:10\">PSA 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:19\">JHN 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:21\">JHN 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2\">JHN 17:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24\">ACT 2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:19–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's power over sin and death remains effective</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:2-Rom8:3\">ROM 8:2–8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:26–7:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's power remains available in human experience</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's forgiving power is effective today</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:23\">JHN 20:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7\">EPH 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's enabling power is effective today</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:18–28:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:14\">JHN 16:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:6\">1CO 12:4–12:6</a></p>",
